com.gridgraph.storage.heap.tuple

Class VertexDegreeDataTuple

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.gridgraph.storage.heap.tuple.HeapDataTuple
      • com.gridgraph.storage.heap.tuple.VertexDegreeDataTuple

  • public class VertexDegreeDataTuple
extends HeapDataTuple
    A VertexDegreeDataTuple represents binary data for degree data of a vertex, read from and written to file or mapped memory
    Data layer for each tuple:
        int value: in degree
        int value: out degree
    Author:
    guobao.chen
